Class GenericListFrag<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
      • mobilesdkdemo.rbbn.itswinter.audio.fragment.GenericListFrag<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, androidx.lifecycle.HasDefaultViewModelProviderFactory, androidx.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, androidx.lifecycle.ViewModelStoreOwner, androidx.savedstate.SavedStateRegistryOwner

    public class GenericListFrag<T>
extends androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
    This GenericListFrag is child class that extends Fragment GenericListFrag is generic class for simple list. GenericListFrag can implement every simple list. GenericListFrag has the field rvList as RecyclerView, the feild layoutManager for RecyclerView.LayoutManager the field myAdapter for GenericAdapter, and layout id of item for list This GenericListFrag need GenericAdapter, layout id of item for list to initialte this.
